# Make GitHub highlight TypeEasy (.te) sources using its TypeScript grammar
# until TypeEasy is registered in github-linguist/linguist.
# TS matches better than JS: let/var/const, class, =>, ${...} interpolation,
# plus type annotations like `: int` / `: string` / `: dynamic`.
*.te linguist-language=TypeScript

# Do not count benchmark/generated .te files in the language stats donut.
benchmarks/**     linguist-vendored
typeeasycode/_*.te linguist-generated
